Bugtracker

Views: 
    Show all the issues
        Order by issues name, date submitted, frequency, and priority
        Comment on existing issues
    Submit new issues
    Close issues
    
Database:
    bugs:   id/name/description/date_submitted/categoryID/frequency/priorityID/userID
    priority:   id/name
    comments:   id/bugID/title/content/typeID/userID
    comment_types:  id/type         ?not sure what this is for?
    categories:     id/category
    
Models:
    issue_model:
        get_all_issues()
        get_active_issues()
        create_issue()
        edit_issue()
        update_issue_status()
        delete_issue()
    comment_model:
        get_comments()
        create_comment()
        edit_comment()
        delete_comment()
